<p><a href="https://www.linuxfromscratch.org/lfs/view/12.4/">Version
12.4</a> of Linux From Scratch (LFS) and Beyond Linux From Scratch
(BLFS) have been <a
href="https://lists.linuxfromscratch.org/sympa/arc/lfs-announce/2025-09/msg00000.html">released</a>. LFS
provides step-by-step instructions on building a customized Linux
system entirely from source, and BLFS helps to extend an LFS
installation into a more usable system. Notable changes in this
release include updates to GNU Binutils 2.45, GCC 15.2, GNU C Library
(glibc) 2.42, and Linux 6.15.1. See the <a
href="https://www.linuxfromscratch.org/lfs/view/12.4/chapter01/changelog.html">Changelog</a>
for all updates since 12.3.</p>
<p></p>